caption:
SAMANA is proud to stand with Dubai Land Department’s She Pioneers initiative — a powerful step toward empowering women across the real estate industry.
From leadership to investment, we believe in creating space for every voice to lead and every talent to thrive.

Thank you to Majida Ali Rashed, CEO – Real Estate Development Sector, Dubai Land Department, for leading this powerful initiative

